This is a list of the currently recognized species in the genus '''''[[Ptilotus]]''.'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.anbg.gov.au/chah/apc/|title=Australian Plant Census|date=23 January 2015|website=Australian Plant Census|publisher=Council of Heads of Australasian Herbaria|access-date=22 January 2017}}</ref> All species are native to [[Mainland Australia|continental Australia]], mostly in the arid regions, though one species also occurs in [[Tasmania]] and another in [[Malesia]].
